</div>","info":{"doc":"A checkpoint in code generation to print all declarations in between\ncompiler passes in order to ease debugging.\nThe trace can be viewed with `set_option trace.Compiler.step true`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Main.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.checkpoint","kind":"def","line":51,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.checkpoint","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Main.lean#L51-L67"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Main.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.shouldGenerateCode\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">shouldGenerateCode</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"We do not generate code for `declName` if\n- Its type is a proposition.\n- Its type is a type former.\n- It is tagged as `[macro_inline]`.\n- It is a type class instance.\n\nRemark: we still generate code for declarations tagged as `[inline]`\nand `[specialize]` since they can be partially applied.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Main.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.shouldGenerateCode","kind":"def","line":21,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.shouldGenerateCode","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Main.lean#L21-L49"}}],"imports":["Lean.Compiler.IR","Lean.Compiler.IR.Basic","Lean.Compiler.LCNF.Check","Lean.Compiler.LCNF.CompilerM","Lean.Compiler.LCNF.Passes","Lean.Compiler.LCNF.SplitSCC","Lean.Compiler.L